Class Jsr330ProcessorImpl

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.hk2.jsr330.spi.internal.Jsr330ProcessorImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Jsr330Processor, PostConstruct
@Service(metadata="service.ranking=-2147483648")
@RunLevel(value=-1)
public class Jsr330ProcessorImpl
extends Object
implements Jsr330Processor, PostConstruct

Default Jsr330Processor for locating and installing all Jsr330Bindings into the currently running habitat. This implementation leverages the RunLevelServicee to be immediately run as part of startup if this module/class is in the classpath.

Since:
3.1
Author:
Jeff Trent
